Description: The European Environment Agency (EEA) is an agency of the European Union. Our task is to provide sound- independent information on the environment. We are a major information source for those involved in developing- adopting- implementing and evaluating environmental policy- and also the general public.The dataset contains metadata for various items published on the portal; reports- articles- speeches- datasets- indicators etc.
